  "remarks": "Kim Sok Chol acted as the DPRK Ambassador to Burma and he operates as a KOMID facilitator.  He was paid by KOMID for his assistance and arranges meetings on behalf of KOMID, including a meeting between KOMID and Burmese defense related persons to discuss financial matters.",
